casebody.data:
Edson Keith v. A. D. Moore et al. Everett, Dellenbaugh & Wood, for plaintiff. Burhe & Ingersoll, for defendant.

Attachment — De-delivery Bond for part of Property attached.

Application for supersedeas.

Held: Under R. S. 5529, defendant has a right to furnish a re-delivery bond for the whole or for a part of the property attached.
